{
  "stem": "1033.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And his face turned into a big grin, and I could feel the blood just-- just drain out of me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I took off like a shot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I ran downstairs.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And when the trials were run in Israel about Eichmann, I recognized that that face and that grin belonged to him.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But at the time, I didn't how it was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I lined up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "About midday we started-- everybody was accounted for.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We started marching into the railway station of the-- of the city of [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we were marched not to the station, but one of the sides, along the station a bit, to one way.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And there was a long line of red cattle cars with a center door, two small windows on each end, a sliding door in the middle.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they started-- as we lined up against the cars, they started loading us on the cars.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And there were maybe 70, 80 people in a car.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And when my turn came, I elbowed and slithered through people who were already in the wagon, and I found a place about the middle of the floor.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I could see the window where I was, stooped down.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But they still kept shoving people on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And people who came on first, who tried to get a corner for themselves or their friends or family, they were squeezed into smaller and smaller and smaller spaces, and they were protesting.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And you know, I just wrote about this, the three days in the wagon, so I don't want to spend too much time on it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyhow, OK.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, it's fairly vivid in my mind because I was thinking about it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People tried to open their suitcases.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Eventually, the door got slung shut, and I could hear the lock snap.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
